STRAIT OF GIBRALTAR.
MORROCCO.
NGA CHART 51160 (21ST ED).
1. NAVIGATION PROHIBITED UNTIL FURTHER NOTICE
   IN AREA BOUND BY
   35-54.6N 005-28.8W, 35-50.3N 005-35.0W,
   35-52.3N 005-35.5W, 35-55.6N 005-28.8W.
   ANY VESSEL INTENDING TO CROSS
   THIS AREA SHOULD CONTACT THE
   MORROCAN MARITIME AUTHORITIES.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 1208/10.
